---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Objectives & Methodology - PROSPERO">
    <!-- Hero: Objectives & Impact -->
    <section class="relative pt-32 pb-section-padding overflow-hidden bg-surface">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-6g-pattern opacity-50 z-0"></div>
        <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-8 relative z-10 text-center">
            <h1 class="font-display-lg text-display-lg tracking-tight text-sovereign-blue mb-stack-md">
                Objectives & Impact
            </h1>
            <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary mx-auto rounded-full mb-stack-lg"></div>
            <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                PROSPERO aims to redefine the landscape of 6G telecommunications through sustainable, transparent, and high-performance network architectures, ensuring European technological sovereignty.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Methodology -->
    <section class="py-section-padding bg-surface-container-lowest">
        <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-8 text-center">
            <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-sovereign-blue mb-stack-md">Methodology</h2>
            
            <div class="relative mt-12">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-glass-stroke shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)] hover:shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] transition-shadow duration-300 relative pt-12">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-eco-surface text-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 shadow-sm border border-primary/20">1</div>
                        <h4 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-background mb-2">Research & Analysis</h4>
                        <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Comprehensive study of current 5G limitations and emerging 6G requirements.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-glass-stroke shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)] hover:shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] transition-shadow duration-300 relative pt-12">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-eco-surface text-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 shadow-sm border border-primary/20">2</div>
                        <h4 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-background mb-2">Architecture Design</h4>
                        <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Developing modular frameworks for dynamic resource integration.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-glass-stroke shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)] hover:shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] transition-shadow duration-300 relative pt-12">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-eco-surface text-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 shadow-sm border border-primary/20">3</div>
                        <h4 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-background mb-2">Simulation & Testing</h4>
                        <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Rigorous evaluation of proposed models using advanced network simulators.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-glass-stroke shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)] hover:shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] transition-shadow duration-300 relative pt-12">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-eco-surface text-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 shadow-sm border border-primary/20">4</div>
                        <h4 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-background mb-2">Deployment & Validation</h4>
                        <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Real-world deployment scenarios to validate system efficiency and scalability.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Project Overview -->
    <section class="py-section-padding bg-surface">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-8">
            <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-sovereign-blue mb-stack-lg text-center">Project Overview</h2>
            <div class="space-y-stack-md text-on-surface-variant font-body-lg text-body-lg">
                <p>
                    The PROSPERO project initiates a transformative approach to mobile infrastructure, aiming to construct a truly global cellular provider model. By integrating commercial entities and Mobile Network Operators (MNOs) through state-of-the-art technologies, PROSPERO facilitates dynamic business collaborations and enables new commercial models.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Building on the foundation laid by previous European projects like ORIGAMI, PROSPERO specifically targets the barriers to entry in the telecommunications market. It provides a robust, scalable architecture that supports the demanding requirements of 6G, while maintaining a strong commitment to environmental sustainability and energy efficiency.
                </p>
                <div class="bg-eco-surface/50 p-8 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-primary my-stack-lg shadow-sm">
                    <p class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary m-0">"Our mission is to architect a transparent, high-frequency network that empowers users while safeguarding ecological boundaries."</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Ethics & Compliance -->
    <section class="py-section-padding bg-surface-container-lowest border-t border-glass-stroke">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-8 text-center">
            <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-sovereign-blue mb-stack-md">Ethics & Compliance</h2>
            <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-stack-lg">
                PROSPERO is deeply committed to upholding the highest standards of ethics, privacy, and regulatory compliance throughout its lifecycle. We strictly adhere to European Union regulations, including GDPR, ensuring that all data handling and network operations are transparent and secure. Our ethics committee oversees operations to maintain these rigorous standards.
            </p>
            <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-surface px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-label-sm text-label-sm font-bold text-sovereign-blue shadow-sm border border-glass-stroke">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">verified_user</span> GDPR Compliant
                </span>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-surface px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-label-sm text-label-sm font-bold text-sovereign-blue shadow-sm border border-glass-stroke">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">policy</span> EU Horizon Standards
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
